One year ago, @HouseDemocrats passed #HR1 – a transformative anti-corruption and clean elections bill. 

@senatemajldr continues to block #HR1. He wants to maintain the corrupt status quo in Washington. 

It’s time for the Senate to vote on #HR1! https://t.co/4G4BxJ6FzH

@HouseDemocrats passed #HR1, the #SAFEAct and the #SHIELDAct to fight foreign interference and protect our country.

President Trump and Congressional Republicans have refused to act.

Their failure to protect our elections is an unconscionable dereliction of duty.
